        public static final java.util.Comparator<ItemStack> TYPE
        Compares ItemStacks based on ItemType. This comparator will not return the same results as ItemStack.equals(ItemStack) for ItemStacks with extra attached data, different damage values, or different sizes.

        public static final java.util.Comparator<ItemStack> DAMAGE
        Compares ItemStacks based on ItemStack damage. This comparator will not return the same results as ItemStack.equals(ItemStack) for ItemStacks with extra attached data, different types, or different sizes.

      • SIZE

        public static final java.util.Comparator<ItemStack> SIZE
        Compares ItemStacks based on ItemStack size. This comparator will not return the same results as ItemStack.equals(ItemStack) for ItemStacks with extra attached data, different types, or different damage values.

      • TYPE_DAMAGE

        public static final java.util.Comparator<ItemStack> TYPE_DAMAGE
        Compares ItemStacks based on ItemType and ItemStack damage. This comparator will not return the same results as ItemStack.equals(ItemStack) for ItemStacks with extra attached data or different sizes.

      • TYPE_SIZE

        public static final java.util.Comparator<ItemStack> TYPE_SIZE
        Compares ItemStacks based on ItemType and ItemStack size. This comparator will not return the same results as ItemStack.equals(ItemStack) for ItemStacks with extra attached data or different damage values.

      • TYPE_DAMAGE_SIZE

        public static final java.util.Comparator<ItemStack> TYPE_DAMAGE_SIZE
        Compares ItemStacks based on ItemType, ItemStack damage and ItemStack size. This comparator will not return the same results as ItemStack.equals(ItemStack) for ItemStacks with extra attached data.
